Socioeconomic status and stroke incidence, prevalence, mortality, and worldwide 
burden: an ecological analysis from the Global Burden of Disease Study 2017.

Avan A(1), Digaleh H(2), Di Napoli M(3), Stranges S(4)(5)(6), Behrouz R(7), 
Shojaeianbabaei G(1), Amiri A(1), Tabrizi R(8)(9), Mokhber N(10)(11), Spence 
