Cost-effectiveness analysis of universal adult immunization with 
tetanus-diphtheria-acellular pertussis vaccine (Tdap) versus current practice in 
Brazil.

Fernandes EG(1), Sartori AMC(2), de Soárez PC(3), Amaku M(4), de Azevedo Neto 
RS(5), Novaes HMD(6).

Author information:
(1)Departamento de Medicina Preventiva, Faculdade de Medicina da Universidade de 
