da Universidade de São Paulo, Av. Dr. Enéas de Carvalho Aguiar, 255, ICHC, 4° 
andar, sala 4028 Cerqueira César, CEP: 05403-000 São Paulo, SP, Brazil; Health 
Technology Assessment Institute (IATS), Brazil. Electronic address: 
